snippet: Sophie Brunner had 18 points, on 8-of-11 shooting, and 10 rebounds, Reili Richardson scored 11 with seven assists and No. 23 Arizona State never trailed in its 79-52 win over Oral Roberts on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: Sophie Brunner had 18 points, on 8-of-11 shooting, and 10 rebounds, Reili Richardson scored 11 with seven assists and No. 23 Arizona State never trailed in its 79-52 win over Oral Roberts on Saturday.

headline.main: Brunner, No. 23 Arizona St Women Beat Oral Roberts 79-52
